        "creation_date": 1318625183,
        "body": "<p>If the <code>remove<\/code> call is, as you say, not operating on the iterated sequence then there must be another thread updating <code>plugin.inreview<\/code>.  <\/p>\n\n<p>Check all write accessors of <code>plugin.review<\/code> and make sure no concurrent update is possible while a thread is reading using this code.  <\/p>\n\n<p>Note that such a bug could fail to manifest for a long time and then suddenly become a serious issue due to changes elsewhere that affect thread timings.<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 7773386,
        "question_id": 7773336
    }],
